check_files.py
=====
- Requirements: pyYaml

check_files will go to all files passed to it and search for 'copy' tasks. If
one is found, it will check if the file(s) really exist.
The script needs to be executed from the root of the repository.

Usage:
check_files.py [--debug] [--ignore-var=] [--print-ignore] files...

validate_yaml.py
=====
- Requirements: pyYaml

validate_yaml will try to load all files specified. If PyYaml throws an exception while loading, then an error message will be printed

Usage:
validate_yaml.py files...
